eck"></t>to check</a></div><div class="col-auto text-end"><span class="o_kanban_monetary"><t t-out="dashboard.to_check_balance"></t></span></div></div></t></div></t><t t-name="JournalBodyGraph"><field name="kanban_dashboard_graph" t-att-graph_type="['cash','bank'].includes(journal_type) ? 'line' : 'bar'" widget="dashboard_graph"></field></t></templates></kanban>